sub_title: Interested in the world of water and the application of GIS.
summary:
Originally from Eritrea and now living in the Netherlands, I am interested in the world around us, specially in water studies and the application of ArcGIS software. Previously achieved a bachelor degree in Geology with a number of years of work experience. In the last five years since I came to the Netherlands, I have done a number of local intensive language courses, successfully finished a masters in Hydrology and recently did a research-internship at a regional water company. My level of Dutch language level has been upgraded to B2. I also did a training in introduction to ArcGIS and use of ArcMAP software at ESRI Nederland in Rotterdam.
ArcGIS 
ArcMAP 10.4 (ArcGIS 10.4)
ArcGIS Pro.
Phyton programming
